extends layouts/layout

block content
  //- include includes/triangles.jade
  include includes/header-light.jade
  #page-content.page-akc
    section#hero.hero-big.parallax-section.text-light(data-parallax-image='img/projects/akc-large.jpg')
      //- .hero-overlay      
      .page-title.hleft
        h5.alttitle Design and Development
        h1
          strong American 
            br
            | Kennel Club
      //- a#scroll-down(href='#') Scroll Down

    section#page-body.body-akc
      .wrapper-small.has-animation
        h4.align-center
          strong Ecommerce
        h6.alttitle.align-center for the largest dog community in the world
        .column-section.clearfix
            p American Kennel Club approached Makeable with a series of projects including an overhaul of their website, several apps, and promotional sites. I was involved in all the projects in different capacities.
            p I worked as a designer on AKC Marketplace, an offshoot of the main site. Marketplace allows vets, groomers, dog walkers, boards, breeders, and pet shops to create their own page to promote their business to the AKC community. 
            //- I did the design, matching the system created for the main site. After creating the main pages as PSDs, I moved to designing in the browser and lead front-end development.

      .wrapper
        .spacer.spacer-big
        .wolf-grid.clearfix(data-mouseparallax='false')
          .wolf-item(data-speed="0")
            .wolf-item-inner
              .wolf-media.portfolio-media.browser-chrome
                .browser-shadow
                  .loader
                  img(data-aload='img/akc/akc_01-medium.jpg' srcset="img/akc/akc_01-small.jpg 640w, img/akc/akc_01-medium.jpg 800w, img/akc/akc_01-large.jpg 1280w" alt='AKC Marketplace Website Dog Listing')
          .wolf-item.is-caption(data-speed="-2")
            .wolf-item-inner
              .wolf-media.portfolio-media
                .figcaption
                  p Marketplace allows businesses to create mini-sites to advertise to the AKC&nbsp;community.
          .wolf-item.is-caption.is-caption--right(data-speed="0")
            .wolf-item-inner
              .wolf-media.portfolio-media
                .figcaption
                  p Search is a major component of the site. It uses a natural language system and featured results that can be&nbsp;sponsored.
          .wolf-item(style='margin-bottom:0')
            .wolf-item-inner
              .wolf-media.portfolio-media.browser-chrome
                .browser-shadow
                  .loader
                  img(data-aload='img/akc/akc_04-medium.jpg' srcset="img/akc/akc_04-small.jpg 640w, img/akc/akc_04-medium.jpg 800w, img/akc/akc_04-large.jpg 1280w" alt='AKC Marketplace Website Search Page')

          .wolf-item.wfull
            .wolf-item-inner
              .wolf-media.portfolio-media
                img.has-animation(src='img/akc/akc_05-medium.png' srcset="img/akc/akc_05-small.png 640w, img/akc/akc_05-medium.png 800w, img/akc/akc_05-large.png 1440w, img/akc/akc_05-xlarge.png 1960w" alt='AKC Marketplace Mobile Site')

        .wrapper-medium.has-animation
          .wolf-item.wfull(style='margin-bottom:0')
            .wolf-item-inner.browser-chrome.is-large
              .wolf-media.portfolio-media.browser-shadow
                a(href='img/akc/akc_02-medium.jpg', data-rel='lightcase:akc')
                  .loader
                  img(src='img/akc/akc_02-medium.jpg' srcset="img/akc/akc_02-small.jpg 640w, img/akc/akc_02-medium.jpg 1000w, img/akc/akc_02-large.jpg 1400w" alt='AKC Marketplace Website Storefront')


      .wrapper-small.has-animation
        .spacer.spacer-medium
        h4.align-center
          strong Social Networking
        h6.alttitle.align-center for dogs
        .column-section.clearfix
            p I was also the front-end developer of Wooftale&mdash;lovingly deemed 'Facebook for Dogs.' The app uses 'if this, then that' logic to measure things like the dog's walking distance and temperature then  posts statuses or 'Wooftales' to the dog's feed. One of the most interesting parts of the app is creating shareable posts via HTML5's canvas. Using javascript to create the canvas, I could take a snapshot and export as a PNG that was shareable to the Wooftale feed as well as Instagram and other social&nbsp;networks.
      .wrapper-mini.has-animation
        .spacer.spacer-small
        h6
          strong Links
        p
          a(href='http://marketplace.akc.org' target='_blank') AKC Marketplace
          br
          a(href='http://caninechronicle.com/breaking-news/akc-launches-marketplace-for-clubs' target='_blank') 
            em AKC Launches Marketplace for Clubs
          br
          a(href='http://wooftale.com' target='_blank') Wooftale Teaser Site

      .wrapper
        .spacer.spacer-medium
        .owl-slider
          figure
            img(src='img/akc/akc_09-medium.jpg' srcset="img/akc/akc_09-small.jpg 640w, img/akc/akc_09-medium.jpg 1000w, img/akc/akc_09-large.jpg 2000w" alt='Dog and Laptop')
            figcaption
             p.slider-caption I was the front-end developer of the Wooftale promotional site.
          figure
            img(data-aload='img/akc/akc_06-medium.jpg' srcset="img/akc/akc_06-small.jpg 640w, img/akc/akc_06-medium.jpg 1000w, img/akc/akc_06-large.jpg 2000w" alt='Mobile Screens')
            figcaption
             p.slider-caption 
                | The left screen shows the feed with an event&nbsp;post. 
                br
                | The right screen shows a&nbsp;'Wooftale' post in the app feed.
          figure
            img(data-aload='img/akc/akc_07-medium.jpg' srcset="img/akc/akc_07-small.jpg 640w, img/akc/akc_07-medium.jpg 1000w, img/akc/akc_07-large.jpg 2000w" alt='Dog and Mobile Instagram')
            figcaption
             p.slider-caption Using HTML's canvas element allowed users to customize the look of the shareable Wooftale. A PNG of the canvas element was then outputted and posted to the feed in the app as well as other social&nbsp;networks.

      .wrapper
        ul.single-pagination
          li.prev
            a(href='artnet.html')
              img(src='img/projects/artnet-small.jpg', alt='prev')
              span Previous Project
          li.backtoworks
            a(href='/') Back To Works
          li.next
            a(href='weather-channel.html' style='background:url("img/twc/rain.gif");background-size:cover;background-position: 50% 100%;')
              img(src='img/projects/twc2.png', alt='next')
              span Next Project